{{Islam}}
Mainstream [[Islamic law]] stipulates detailed regulations for the use of violence, including the use of violence [[Islam and domestic violence|within the family or household]], the use of [[Hudud|corporal and capital punishment]], as well as how, when and against whom to [[Islam and war|wage war]].

